{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845115093,"sessionID":"ses_287621e35ffeBybyIcGCUlmjbj","part":{"id":"prt_d789e0485001P5DNSyoKuQ8Cwh","messageID":"msg_d789df451001R6glEl0iVR7jHr","sessionID":"ses_287621e35ffeBybyIcGCUlmjbj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-51c0b8b53ecc475ea4b302fefb0728e0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Implementation Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n4: **Language**: Go\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n7: \n8: ## Task Breakdown\n9: \n10: ### Task 1: Create package structure and initialize controller module\n11: - [ ] Verify `pkg/workloadmanager/controller` directory exists\n12: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/controller.go` - SandboxController structure and lifecycle\n13: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_builder.go` - Sandbox CR building utilities\n14: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/session_manager.go` - Session lifecycle management\n15: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/entrypoint.go` - EntryPoint construction\n16: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/utils.go` - Utility functions (random string, name generation)\n17: - [ ] Verify package compiles: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller`\n18: \n19: **Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller` to ensure the package structure is valid\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ### Task 2: Implement K8sClient for Sandbox operations\n24: - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/client/k8s_client.go` - Kubernetes client for Sandbox operations\n25: - [ ] Define K8sClient struct\n26:   - [ ] `clientset *clientset.Clientset` - Kubernetes clientset\n27: