n**: All tests pass, code is linted, packages build successfully\n542: \n543: ---\n544: \n545: ## Summary\n546: \n547: **Total Tasks**: 20\n548: **Estimated Effort**: M (Medium) - 10-15 hours\n549: \n550: ### Key Deliverables\n551: 1. **SandboxController** - Core sandbox creation and lifecycle management\n552: 2. **K8sClient** - Kubernetes integration for Sandbox operations\n553: 3. **HTTP Handler Layer** - REST API for sandbox operations\n554: 4. **API Types** - Request/response types for external API\n555: 5. **Internal Types** - Internal data structures\n556: 6. **Utilities** - Helper functions for name generation, conversion\n557: 7. **Session Management** - Session storage and retrieval\n558: 8. **Error Handling** - Unified error handling and response formatting\n559: 9. **Validation** - Request validation\n560: 10. **Tests** - Comprehensive unit and integration tests\n561: 11. **Documentation** - API documentation and usage guide\n562: \n563: ### Success Criteria\n564: - All unit tests pass with >80% code coverage\n565: - All integration tests pass\n566: - AgentRuntime Sandbox creation works end-to-end\n567: - CodeInterpreter Sandbox creation works end-to-end\n568: - Session query and deletion work correctly\n569: - Error handling returns appropriate HTTP status codes\n570: - Resources are properly cleaned up on errors and timeouts\n571: - Code passes static analysis and linting\n572: - Documentation is complete and accurate\n573: \n574: ### Dependencies\n575: - Go 1.24+\n576: - Kubernetes cluster (for testing)\n577: - Redis/Valkey (for session store)\n578: - agent-sandbox CRD (agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1)\n579: - AgentRuntime CRD (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1)\n580: - CodeInterpreter CRD (runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1)\n581: - k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1\n582: - k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n583: - gin-gonic/gin (HTTP framework)\n584: - go-redis/v9 or valkey-go (Redis client)\n585: \n586: ### Blocked By\n587: - None (design stage ST-3 completed)\n588: \n589: ### Blocks\n590: - None (this is a foundational component)\n\n(End of file - total 590 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005 — Sandbox 创建处理器 Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`\n**Language**: Go\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Create package structure and initialize controller module\n- [ ] Verify `pkg/workloadmanager/controller` directory exists\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/controller.go` - SandboxController structure and lifecycle\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_builder.go` - Sandbox CR building utilities\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/session_manager.go` - Session lifecycle management\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/entrypoint.go` - EntryPoint construction\n- [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/utils.go` - Utility functions (random string, name generation)\n- [ ] Verify package compiles: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller`\n\n**Verification**: Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller` to ensure the package structure is valid\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775845115054,"end":1775845115089}}}}
